==English==
{{wikipedia|dab=free}}

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|fre||lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|frēo}}, {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{term/t|gem-pro|*frijaz}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{term/t|ine-pro|*prei-||to be fond of}}, {{term/t|ine-pro|*prey-}}. Compare West Frisian {{term|frij|lang=fy}}, Dutch {{term|vrij|lang=nl}}, German {{term|frei|lang=de}}, Danish {{term|fri|lang=da}}.

The verb comes from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|frēoġan}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/fɹiː/}}
* {{audio|en-us-free.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{audio|En-uk-free.ogg|Audio (UK)}}
* {{rhymes|iː}}

